                <article class="post-7031 page type-page status-publish hentry">

                    <section class="entry">
	                	<h1>The これ, それ, あれ Quiz</h1>
<h4>&ldquo;Cheating on a quiz show? That&#8217;s sort of like plagiarizing a comic strip.&rdquo; <span style="color: #888888;">- Paul Scofield</span></h4>
<p>Now it&#8217;s time to mix things up a little bit. Instead of having you do entire sentences, or translating things, I just want you to fill in the blank. The blank, of course, is going to be either これ, それ, or あれ. Up to the challenge? I think it&#8217;ll help you figure out which one to use when a lot better. Let&#8217;s give it a shot.</p>
<hr class="d4pbbc-hr" />
<p>You: ____　は　あさごはん　ですか？　Is that breakfast? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink268369672" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet268369672'))">Answer → </a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet268369672"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet268369672'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink268369672'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">それ, which refers to something that the person the speaker is talking to has. </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<p>Person B: はい、____　は　あさごはん　です。Yes, this is breakfast. <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink823735805" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet823735805'))">Answer → </a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet823735805"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet823735805'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink823735805'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">これ, which refers to something the speaker has in their possession. </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<p>You: ____　は　いす　ですか？　Is this a chair? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink2086143993" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet2086143993'))">Answer → </a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet2086143993"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet2086143993'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink2086143993'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">これ </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<p>Person B: いいえ、____　は　いす　じゃありません。　No, that is not a chair. <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink1223494788" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet1223494788'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet1223494788"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet1223494788'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink1223494788'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">それ </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<p>You: ____　は　じてんしゃ　ですか？　Is that over there a bike? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink898307223" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet898307223'))">Answer → </a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet898307223"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet898307223'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink898307223'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">あれ, which refers to something away from both the speaker and the person being spoken to </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<p>Person B: はい、_____　は　じてんしゃ　です。<a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink295751842" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet295751842'))">Answer → </a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet295751842"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet295751842'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink295751842'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">あれ, you can base this answer off the previous answer (previous fill-in-the-blank), since that one was あれ (away from both people) as well. </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<p>Person B: ____　は　のみもの　です。This is a beverage. <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink2141207884" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet2141207884'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet2141207884"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet2141207884'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink2141207884'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">これ </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<p>You: _____　は　のみもの　ですか？ Is that a beverage? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink704638846" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet704638846'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet704638846"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet704638846'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink704638846'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">それ </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<p>Person B: はい、____　は　のみもの　です。Yes, this is a beverage. <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink428536160" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet428536160'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet428536160"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet428536160'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink428536160'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">これ </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<p>You: いいえ、____　は　のみもの　じゃありません。____ は　のみもの　です。No, that is not a beverage. <em>That</em> (over there) is a beverage. <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink1960212398" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet1960212398'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet1960212398"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet1960212398'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink1960212398'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">1. それ　2. あれ </div></p>
<div class="woo-sc-divider"></div>
<div class="woo-sc-box tick   ">What are the differences between これ, それ, and あれ? Make sure you can explain the differences (possibly out loud?) before moving on to the next page. In theory, you should have these down pretty well by now, if not, go back and review!</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="btn large" style="margin-right: 5px;" href="../8-6/index.html#top">← 後</a><a class="btn large primary" href="../8-8/index.html#top">前 →</a></p>
	               	</section><!-- /.entry -->

					
